
---------------------------------------------------------
HOW TO CREATE LOGIN PAGE USING HTML5 & CSS3
---------------------------------------------------------

REQUIRED
---------------------------------------------------------

1.login.html
2.login.css
3.avatar logo
4.user and password avatar
5.Images folder

STEPS
---------------------------------------------------------

1.Create a html file and name it "login.html".
2.Create the logo avatar field.
2.Create username and password input fields.
3.Insert user and password avatars.
4.Create submit button.
5.Create Copyright and Year of copyright Using Javascript date/time functions.
6.Do css styling to make the form presentable. 

---------------------------------------------------------
     --------THE END--------
